1. *Osetila* sam promenu u vazduhu. (I *felt* a change in the air.)
2. Ona je već duže vreme *osećala* da nešto nije u redu. (She had been *feeling* that something was wrong for a while now.)
3. Kada je *osećala* njegov pogled na sebi, znala je da mora da ode. (When she *felt* his gaze on her, she knew she had to leave.)
4. *Osetio* sam lagani dodir na ramenu. (I *felt* a gentle touch on my shoulder.)
5. Ona nije mogla da *oseća* miris zbog prehlade. (She couldn't *smell* because of a cold.)
6. Kada je *osećao* da mu se gubi tlo pod nogama, potražio je pomoć. (When he *felt* like the ground was slipping under his feet, he sought help.)
7. Kao dete, često sam *osećao* strah kada bih bio sam kod kuće. (As a child, I often *felt* scared when I was home alone.)
8. Uvek sam *osećala* olakšanje kada bih se vratila kući. (I always *felt* relieved when I would come back home.)